quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  44,30,wlqd njjayna bani 'iisrayiyl min aleadhab almudhll lahum biqatl abnayhm waistikhdam nsayhm
  44,31,"mn frewn, 'iinah kan jbarana min almshrkyn, msrfana fi alelw waltkbr ealaa eibad allh"
  44,32,wlqd astafayna bani 'iisrayiyl ealaa eilm minaa bihim ealaa ealamiun zmanhm
  44,33,watynahm min almejzat ealaa yd musaa ma fih abtlawhm wakhtbarhm rukha'an wshdt
  44,34,"'iina hwla' almushrikin min qawmik -ayha alrswl- lyqwlwn: ma hi 'iilaa mawtatuna alty nmwtha, wahi almawtat al'uwlaa walakhyrt, wama nahn baed mmatna bimabeuthin llhsab walthwab waleqab"
  44,35,"'in hwla' almushrikin min qawmik -ayha alrswl- lyqwlwn: ma hi 'iilaa mawtatuna alty nmwtha, wahi almawtat al'uwlaa walakhyrt, wama nahn baed mmatna bimabeuthin llhsab walthwab waleqab"
  44,36,"wyqwlwn aydana: fati- ya muhamad 'ant wman mek- biabayina aladhin qad matu، 'iin kuntum sadiqin fi 'ana allah yabeath man fi alqubur ahya'"
  44,37,"ahwla' almushrikun khayr 'am qawm tubbae alhimyary waladhin min qablihim min al'umam alkafrt brbha? 'ahlaknahum l'ijramhm wkfrhm, lays hwla' almushrikun bikhayr min awlykm fnsfh enhm, wala nhlkhm, wahum biallah kafrwn"
  44,38,"wma khalaqna alsamawat wal'ard wabaynahuma lebana, ma khalaqnahuma 'iilaa bialhaqi aldhy hu sunat allah fi khalqih wtdbyruh, wlkn 'akthar hwla' almushrikin la yaelamun dhlk, flhdha lm yatafakaruu fyhma; li'anahum la yarjun thwabana wala yakhafun eqabana"
  44,39,"wma khalaqna alsamawat wal'ard wabaynahuma lebana, ma khalaqnahuma 'iilaa bialhaqi aldhy hu sunat allah fi khalqih wtdbyruh, wlkn 'akthar hwla' almushrikin la yaelamun dhlk, flhdha lm yatafakaruu fyhma; li'anahum la yarjun thwabana wala yakhafun eqabana"
  44,40,'in yawm alqada' bayn alkhalq bima qddamu fi dnyahm min khayr 'aw sharun hu miqatuhum ajmeyn
  44,41,"ywm la yadfae sahib ean sahibuh shyyana, wala yansur bedhm bedana, 'iilaa man rahim allah min almwmnyn, fa'iinah qad yashfae lah eind rabih baed 'iidhan allah lh. 'iina allah hu aleaziz fi antqamh min aedayh, alrahim bawlyayh wa'ahl taeth"
  44,42,"yawm la yadfae sahib ean sahibuh shyyana, wala yansur bedhm bedana, 'iilaa man rahim allah min almwmnyn, fa'iinah qad yashfae lah eind rabih baed 'iidhan allah lh. 'iina allah hu aleaziz fi antqamh min aedayh, alrahim bawlyayh wa'ahl taeth"